==========================================================
  ONE STEP: INSTALL R (if you don't already have it)
==========================================================

  R is the only requirement.

    macOS:    https://cran.r-project.org/bin/macosx/
    Windows:  https://cran.r-project.org/bin/windows/base/
    Linux:    sudo dnf install R       (Fedora/RHEL)
              sudo apt install r-base  (Ubuntu/Debian)
              sudo pacman -S r         (Arch)

==========================================================
  HOW TO RUN — MACOS
==========================================================

  1. Unzip this folder.
  2. Double-click START_HERE.command.
  3. Answer the yes/no questions.

  Gatekeeper note: if blocked on first run, right-click
  START_HERE.command, choose Open, and confirm.

==========================================================
  HOW TO RUN — WINDOWS
==========================================================

  1. Unzip this folder.
  2. Double-click START_HERE.bat.
  3. Answer the yes/no questions.

  SmartScreen note: if blocked, click More info, then
  Run anyway.

==========================================================
  HOW TO RUN — LINUX
==========================================================

  1. Unzip this folder.
  2. Open terminal in that folder.
  3. Run:  ./start_here.sh

